@justaboyinhoodie - NTR is where the MC’s partner is stolen from them by someone else. As such, it really depends on the story’s perspective. From the GF’s view, it’s NTR since her BF was stolen by the sister. From the BF point of view, it’s just cheating. Since the BF is the MC in this story and it’s told from his perspective, it isn’t considered NTR. Similarly, an NTR story told from the perspective of the person doing the stealing is called ‘Netori’.
